{"tid":641692,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞恊杯Ｉ組] 20:00 澳門賓菲加 對 4.25體育團(北韓)","createTime":"2018-04-25T07:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T09:13:22.000Z","uid":78873,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c08c2ccf574ad143b31bcf0c1d379c6a262ea54b","tid":641692,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/31337875_1699405363484358_3420119788330728178_n.png?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=ff3d4c4332cac05ed98f8498d23596d5&amp;oe=5B62165D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F31337875_1699405363484358_3420119788330728178_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Dff3d4c4332cac05ed98f8498d23596d5%26oe%3D5B62165D&h=91052fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">目前小組形勢</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/154338_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F154338_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=d8406ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">過去三場小組賽比數</span></strong></span><br />\n賓菲加 3 - 2 航源 (我島)<br />\n火炬體育團 (北韓) 2 - 3 賓菲加<br />\n4.25體育團 (北韓) 8 - 0 賓菲加<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/04/13/20/3325CC6400000578-0-image-a-34_1460574352740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F04%2F13%2F20%2F3325CC6400000578-0-image-a-34_1460574352740.jpg&h=e0ac925b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>賓菲加勁揪！Ｆｏｒｚａ　Ｂｅｎｆｉｃａ～</strong></span>"},{"pid":"22dafd6fc717e0f1669eb058483bd89cef7bb171","tid":641692,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"澳門賓菲加General Manager Duarte Alves: 我們為澳門足球而戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.offside.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/BenficaMacau_AFCCup2018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.offside.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FBenficaMacau_AFCCup2018.jpg&h=39a78eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文轉自Fox Sports Asia專訪:<br />\nEver since we&rsquo;ve tried to join these Asian competitions we&rsquo;ve been doing it for Macau football not just the club.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">By playing at this level we&rsquo;re trying to motivate the other local clubs to follow our path for more professional or organised and competitive football</span> and being able to see a thousand more people at the stadium for the AFC Cup match with everyone shouting and celebrating together gave me a sense that this is not about the club but about Macau football and the messages of support we&rsquo;ve got truly represents that.<br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;m honoured that we&rsquo;re able to bring this joy and competitiveness to Macau football fans because we&rsquo;re trying to promote our region and our homeland.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.foxsportsasia.com/football/asian-football/afc-cup/827320/benfica-de-macau-taking-asian-football-storm-afc-cup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxsportsasia.com%2Ffootball%2Fasian-football%2Fafc-cup%2F827320%2Fbenfica-de-macau-taking-asian-football-storm-afc-cup%2F&d=mamiB8kKqeBR%2BeAuePE5xNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d5738cf1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.foxsportsasia.com/football/asian-football/afc-cup/827320/benfica-de-macau-taking-asian-football-storm-afc-cup/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">!For the good of Macau!</span></span>"},{"pid":"9914794a1d3940ee0ddfdba1dffb208872f8b378","tid":641692,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"亞洲高水平賽事大戰連場，<br />\n一定好刺激<img src=\"/asse